{"tid":615490,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朱千雪感激父母管得嚴好家教　去男友屋企食飯例必主動執枱洗碗","createTime":"2018-04-03T12:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T15:47:21.000Z","uid":9573,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"51cf82869301888b89654162b0df3c53bfb45452","tid":615490,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1322332/org/17d92864883a706e9d3991d7f2b6ccee.jpg/i10pRJfSfrSqPzucr10Syyln201g0aZfA92CqgPdgqo?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1322332%2Forg%2F17d92864883a706e9d3991d7f2b6ccee.jpg%2Fi10pRJfSfrSqPzucr10Syyln201g0aZfA92CqgPdgqo%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ef30ee6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪會同岑杏賢一齊主持big big channel節目幫手執枱洗碗。<br />\n<br />\n朱千雪 (Tracy) 出席無綫big big channel活動同小朋友一齊玩遊戲，提到近日有報道一個嫲嫲帶孫女出街時，因為孫女扭計買糖，嫲嫲竟怒打孫女，更兜腳踢，引起網民熱烈討論。Tracy表示自己無見過人在公眾地方打小朋友，但就見過一些父母好惡咁喝罵個小朋友，她都會忍唔住望一望。Tracy當然不贊成這些咁極端的管教方式，認為小朋友要從小教導，但不應吓吓打罵，一定要取得平衡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1322342/org/e6d04fa91caa0cb3f5e50c95ac711f7d.jpg/rRtzzpAEvWGPH8ev41_9IaafBByDwSEkzmrpDc5q6Q0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1322342%2Forg%2Fe6d04fa91caa0cb3f5e50c95ac711f7d.jpg%2FrRtzzpAEvWGPH8ev41_9IaafBByDwSEkzmrpDc5q6Q0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=cc2d0072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n千雪話小朋友一定要教幫手執枱洗碗。<br />\n<br />\nTracy說：「我自己父母管教好嚴厲，佢哋無打過我，但係喺教育我哋三姊妹方面做得好好。有啲小朋友出街食飯時喺度喊，可以帶出餐廳外面畀佢企，等佢喊完先返返入去，自己細個嗰時都係咁，唔好騷擾到人哋。我好開心爹地媽咪家教咁好，家庭教育真係好緊要，就算我依家咁大個人，佢哋都會時時提醒我，好多生活上嘅嘢例如喺人屋企食飯要幫手執枱洗碗，食飯要叫人，揸筷子要揸得啱等等。我次次去男朋友屋企食飯都會主動幫手執枱洗碗。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1322345/org/f1dcd1c833efbb2199b25cc1ef663623.jpg/KCfIB_pDOvtwitFkCN-99I44LzU1ThG-RBGIm0QRiJs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1322345%2Forg%2Ff1dcd1c833efbb2199b25cc1ef663623.jpg%2FKCfIB_pDOvtwitFkCN-99I44LzU1ThG-RBGIm0QRiJs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ab722309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTracy覺得爸媽教得佢好好幫手執枱洗碗。<br />\n<br />\nTracy認為小朋友從細個就要開始教，對於有些人覺得「佢哋咁細個唔識㗎，大個先教幫手執枱洗碗啦」，她並不認同：「唔會唔識，就算細個唔識都可以做咗先，例如要雙手接嘢或者畀嘢人，我細個都唔明點解，但都做咗先，大咗自然會明自，原來咁樣係尊重人同有禮貌。」她笑言父母經常對她的提點亦令她有壓力要做好自己：「總之我一定唔會失禮人一定會幫手執碗洗碗。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1322352/org/35cc0e44705095e0a04e7d00a0751b5d.jpg/9qgXlFv01lsl_EXy2WEwrKZk5e9pzW98j_qdW4_6nVs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1322352%2Forg%2F35cc0e44705095e0a04e7d00a0751b5d.jpg%2F9qgXlFv01lsl_EXy2WEwrKZk5e9pzW98j_qdW4_6nVs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=a4ef3797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n千雪去男友屋企食飯一定會幫手執碗洗碗。"},{"pid":"d9a1b9f7ff61ef40a697074d73ec3a50f19170c5","tid":615490,"uid":174074,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:11:32.000Z","msg":"這些機會"},{"pid":"28ee95dc8319d30a90eeb740da2372df64789261","tid":615490,"uid":82532,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://replygif.net/i/759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Freplygif.net%2Fi%2F759.gif&h=54107d82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a0a39bc8aa3d2a416e99be3e4f48b03983dd341","tid":615490,"uid":106675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:13:29.000Z","msg":"去男友屋企扑嘢呢"},{"pid":"8f877799f8e73c2b9c13e0a3b65539d8aeda132c","tid":615490,"uid":9231,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:17:20.000Z","msg":"我老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f51df2f578090e4d9595649adaa8825e383a56","tid":615490,"uid":34000,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T12:26:25.000Z","msg":"成篇報導居然咁正常無彩蛋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a996b45cdd6c9794f33cf835684264746ea394d0","tid":615490,"uid":61130,"